<p>Hi, [<$I2_USER->name>]!<br />
Please follow these instructions in order to guarantee yourself a prom ticket as well as (if applicable) a ticket for your non-senior or non-TJ date.</p>
<form action="[<$I2_ROOT>]prom" method="post">
        <p>Would you like to secure <b><i>your</i> FREE ticket</b> to this year's prom on Friday, June 8th?<br />
	NOTE: If you are taking someone who is also a TJ senior, you do not need to worry about getting them a ticket.<br />
	<input type="radio" name="attending" value="1" />Yes&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
	<input type="radio" name="attending" value="0" checked="checked" />No</p>
	
	<p>Would you like to reserve a ticket for a <b>non-senior TJ student</b>?<br />
	<input type="radio" name="nosenior" value="1" />Yes&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
	<input type="radio" name="nosenior" value="0" checked="checked" />No<br /><br />
	If yes, then please enter that student's name and grade below:<br />
	Name: <input type="text" name="datename" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
	Grade: <input type="text" name="dategrade" size="2" /></p>
	
	<p>Would you like to reserve a ticket for a <b>student who attends another FCPS high school or local private school</b>?<br />
	<input type="radio" name="notj" value="1" />Yes&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
	<input type="radio" name="notj" value="0" checked="checked" />No<br /><br />
	If yes, then please enter that student's name, grade, and school below:<br />
	Name: <input type="text" name="date2name" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
	Grade: <input type="text" name="date2grade" size="2" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
	School: <input type="text" name="date2school" /><br />
	NOTE: You must also print out <a href="http://leadership.tjhsst.edu/2007/Prom%20guest%20form%202007.doc">this form</a> and give it to your date to bring to their school. They must get the correct permissions from their administrators/principals before you are officially allowed to bring them to prom.  Please follow the instructions in the form.</p>
	
	<p>Would you like to reserve a ticket for a person who <b>does not attend high school</b> (college/employed) or who <b>attends a non-local private school</b>?<br />
	<input type="radio" name="nosch" value="1" />Yes&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
	<input type="radio" name="nosch" value="0" checked="checked" />No<br /><br />
	If yes, then please enter the person's name, and a brief description below:<br />
	Name: <input type="text" name="date3name" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
	Description: <input type="text" name="date3desc" /><br />
	NOTE: Please also print out <a href="http://leadership.tjhsst.edu/2007/Prom%20guest%20form%202007.doc">this form</a> and give it to your date.  They must follow the instructions stated at the bottom: simply fill out the appropriate contact information and bring appropriate ID.</p>
	
	<p>Permission forms MUST be turned in with $50 for the non-TJ senior ticket in order for them to be properly processed.<br />
	Forms are due <b>Friday, June 1, 2007</b> to the box outside room 205.<br /><br />
	Questions?  Contact <a href="mailto:robert.svestka@gmail.com">Robert Svestka</a>, <a href="mailto:e_hillenbrand07@yahoo.com">Emily Hillenbrand</a>, or <a href="mailto:the.amz@gmail.com">Amy Friedlander</a>.</p>
        <p><input name="Submit" type="submit" value="Submit" /></p>
</form>
